column5: Thought i'd share! Took this sped up "time lapse" style video launching at Deception and cruising across Lac Seul from earlier this month. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfcGS1nEEQU
Very cool. Did you go up through the rags?
Sure looked like it. The rags would have been towards the very end of the video....tall tree stumps on the right of the boat. PjShorthorn
Cool video, looks like you stay where I stay and I think you passed me on the water. LM
That brings back some found memories of my annual trip.
I meant to multi-quote you, but looks like I goofed up the formatting. No kidding?? Where do you stay? and where (time stamp?) did we pass you on the video? That's pretty cool...
I'll have a lot of fun watching this again come December / January
